T02TD2472E:146b-42: ji lta'i dgongs rgyud de dang des //
T02TD2472E:146b-43: slob ma rnams ni yongs smin bya //

T02TD2472E:146b-47: mngon du phyogs dang bdud bzhi ni //
T02TD2472E:146b-48: 'joms pa'i nus pas brjod pa ste //
T02TD2472E:146b-49: phreng bsam dag dri ma dang //
T02TD2472E:146b-50: mos pa'i spyod pas sgrib pa 'khru //
T02TD2472E:147a-2: 'bras bu mthong ba'i lam la phyogs //
T02TD2472E:147a-3: yi dam dngos grub nye ba yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-4: gzung 'dzin phung po'i bdud rnams bcom //
T02TD2472E:147a-5: chu dang dbu rgyan gyi nus pas //
T02TD2472E:147a-7: sa ni dang po'i sgrib pa dag / las ni rdo rje rin chen gyis //
T02TD2472E:147a-8: rigs kyi nga rgyal byed ba yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-9: 'bras bu bsgom lam phyogs pa dang //
T02TD2472E:147a-10: rdo rje dang ni rin chen gyi //
T02TD2472E:147a-11: thun mong dngos grub pa yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-12: nyon mongs pa yi bdud rnams bcom //
T02TD2472E:147a-13: rdo rje dril bu bdag po yis //
T02TD2472E:147a-14: g-yeng ba lnga yi dri ma 'khru //
T02TD2472E:147a-15: sa gnyis pa nas brgyad pa yi //
T02TD2472E:147a-16: bar gyi sgrib pa sbyangs pa yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-17: padma las dang sangs rgyas kyi //
T02TD2472E:147a-18: rigs kyi nga rgyal las byed yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-19: 'bras bu mthar phyin la phyogs shing //
T02TD2472E:147a-20: gsum po'i thun mong grub pa yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-21: 'chi bdag bdud bcom tshe la dbang //
T02TD2472E:147a-22: brtan byed dbang gi rim pa yis//
T02TD2472E:147a-23: g-yeng ba phra mo'i dri ma 'khru //
T02TD2472E:147a-24: sa bcu'i sgrib pa dag par byed //
T02TD2472E:147a-25: las ni brten par byed pa ste //
T02TD2472E:147a-26: brtul zhugs kyis ni me tog brtan //
T02TD2472E:147a-27: chu dang dbu rgyan dam tshig gis //
T02TD2472E:147a-28: bum pa brtan par bka' stsal gyi //
T02TD2472E:147a-29: rdo rje dril bu lung bstan gyis //
T02TD2472E:147a-30: dbugs phyung bas ni bdag po'o //
T02TD2472E:147a-31: yang na kun gyis thams cad do //
T02TD2472E:147a-32: sangs rgyas sa la mngon phyogs dang //
T02TD2472E:147a-34: lha yi bdud gcod bum pa yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-35: 'bras bu bzhi ni me tog la'o //
T02TD2472E:147a-36: rgyu mthun chu dang dbu rgyan gyis //
T02TD2472E:147a-37: rdo rje dril bu rnam smin yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-38: skyes bu byed pa ming gis te //
T02TD2472E:147a-39: brtan pa dri med 'bras bu ste //
T02TD2472E:147a-40: yang na 'bras bzhi bstan zhes pa'o //
T02TD2472E:147a-41: rgyud las gsungs pa'i yon tan ni //
T02TD2472E:147a-42: bsam yas ji snyed bstan pa kun //
T02TD2472E:147a-43: dbang gi 'bras rab yin par gsungs //
T02TD2472E:147a-45: dbang thob rgyu ni yon yin te //
T02TD2472E:147a-46: ji ltar rgyud lus gsungs pa yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-47: las kyi dang por dbang bya ba //
T02TD2472E:147a-48: dang po'i dbang du gsungs pa yin //
T02TD2472E:147a-49: gnyis pa gsang ba bshad bya ste //
T02TD2472E:147a-50: kye ho ston pa rdo rje 'dzin //
T02TD2472E:147a-52: 'khor rnams bsdu ba rnam mdzad nas //
T02TD2472E:147b-0: yum gyi gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor @147b du //
T02TD2472E:147b-1: gsang ba byang chub sems rab bskur //
T02TD2472E:147b-2: de ltar dpal 'dus la sogs pa'i //
T02TD2472E:147b-3: rgyud rgyal kun la grags pa rnams //
T02TD2472E:147b-4: gleng gzhi zhes su rnam par bshad //
T02TD2472E:147b-5: gnas ni bud med dkyil yin te //
T02TD2472E:147b-6: lhan cig skyes dang zhing skyes dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-7: sngags skyes pa zhes grags pa la //
T02TD2472E:147b-8: sme sha can dang mthu chen dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-9: gar mkhan bco blag mkhan la sogs //
T02TD2472E:147b-10: so so'i rgyud la grags pa yi //
T02TD2472E:147b-11: ji ltar rigs kyi rjes mthun pa'i //
T02TD2472E:147b-12: shes rgyud sbyangs shing yon tan ldan //
T02TD2472E:147b-13: byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas bya ste //
T02TD2472E:147b-14: sangs rgyas gtso bo'i yum du gzung //
T02TD2472E:147b-15: bum pa'i dbang rnams rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-17: bla ma yum gyi gnang ba ni //
T02TD2472E:147b-18: gnyis pa'i dus su rnam par brtag / slob dpon rnam pa gsum du shes //
T02TD2472E:147b-19: dang po thabs mchog yab kyis te //
T02TD2472E:147b-20: gnyis pa gsang ba'i gzungs ma la'o //
T02TD2472E:147b-21: gsum pa gnyis su med pas bya'o //
T02TD2472E:147b-22: slob ma bum dbang rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-23: snying po bzlas pas byed pa dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-24: brtul zhugs dam tshig 'dod pas bya'o //
T02TD2472E:147b-25: dkyil 'khor lus su gsungs pa dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-27: de yang lus kyi dkyil 'khor dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-28: lha yi mtshan nyid shes bya ste //
T02TD2472E:147b-29: lus ni 'dom gang gru bzhi pa'o //
T02TD2472E:147b-30: yang na grub bzhi 'byung ba bzhi //
T02TD2472E:147b-32: tshon sna kha dog sna lnga'o //
T02TD2472E:147b-33: yang na bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
T02TD2472E:147b-34: rtsa ni thig gi rang bzhin te //

T02TD2472E:147b-36: yan lag rta babs mtshan nyid de //
T02TD2472E:147b-37: so sen pa sbu tva ra brgyad //
T02TD2472E:147b-38: snying ni dbus kyi lte ba ste //
T02TD2472E:147b-39: rgyud gang dang ni rjes mthun sbyar //
T02TD2472E:147b-40: lha yi phung po lnga gtso bo //
T02TD2472E:147b-41: 'byung ba lha mor shes par bya //
T02TD2472E:147b-42: khams dang skye mched mang po kun //
T02TD2472E:147b-43: sems dpa' sems mar rab tu grags //
T02TD2472E:147b-44: bud med dkyil 'khor du gsungs te //
T02TD2472E:147b-45: bha ga gzhal yas brtsegs par bstan //
T02TD2472E:147b-46: de la gzung ba'i cho ga dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-47: spyang dang brtag dang byin brlab dang //
T02TD2472E:147b-48: rgyan dang ldan zhing bdug pas bdug / phyi nang khrus byas lha rnams dbab //
T02TD2472E:147b-49: tshogs kyi 'khor los mchod byas la //
T02TD2472E:148a-2: de la chang yang drang bar bya'o //
T02TD2472E:148a-3: de la 'jug pa'i rim pa yang //
T02TD2472E:148a-4: bum pa'i bya ba yang bya ste //
T02TD2472E:148a-5: yol bas bar du bcad nas ni //
T02TD2472E:148a-6: gsol gdab de yi ngo yang dgab //
T02TD2472E:148a-7: me tog byin ta drangs nas su //
T02TD2472E:148a-8: dkyil 'khor bskor nas phyag gsum btsal //
T02TD2472E:148a-9: nang gi dam tshig brtul zhugs sbyin //
T02TD2472E:148a-10: de bzhin dbab pa yang byas nas //
T02TD2472E:148a-11: me tog dor te mthong ba dri //
T02TD2472E:148a-12: lha dang chos kyi tshig phye ste //
T02TD2472E:148a-13: lus kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bstan //
T02TD2472E:148a-14: legs par mthong ba'i 'og tu ni //
T02TD2472E:148a-15: mdun na gnas pa de nyid la //
T02TD2472E:148a-16: gsang ba'i dbang gis sbyor byas te //
T02TD2472E:148a-17: dam tshig 'khor lo drug rim gyis //
T02TD2472E:148a-18: khu ba phyung ste dbang bskur bya //
T02TD2472E:148a-19: dkar dmar spel ba phreng ba'i dbang //
T02TD2472E:148a-20: shu kra zhes te chu yi dbang //
T02TD2472E:148a-21: tshangs sgor mi bskyod dbu rgyan dbang //
T02TD2472E:148a-22: lce la rdo rje de rdo rje //
T02TD2472E:148a-23: rdor bu ma h'um sgra dril bu'i dbang //
T02TD2472E:148a-24: aa ho su kha ming gi dbang //
T02TD2472E:148a-25: dam tshig lces len brtul zhugs dbang //
T02TD2472E:148a-26: blta bar mi bya lung bstan dbang //
T02TD2472E:148a-27: longs spyod rtsar sbyar phyir mi ldog / bde bas bde thabs dbugs dbyung ba'o //
T02TD2472E:148a-28: 'di kun gsang bar bstan pas na //
T02TD2472E:148a-29: gsang ba'i dbang zhes bstan pa yin //
T02TD2472E:148a-30: gsang ba la yang gsum du ste //
T02TD2472E:148a-31: phyi dang nang dang sbas pa'o //
T02TD2472E:148a-32: ga bur tsandan bcu phyed bcas //
T02TD2472E:148a-33: sbom po dang ni dbang mo'i rtses //
T02TD2472E:148a-34: slob ma'i kha ru dbab pa phyi'o //
T02TD2472E:148a-35: slob ma'i dus nyid mnan byas te //
T02TD2472E:148a-36: kha yi thad dkar gnyis sbyar nas //
T02TD2472E:148a-37: ra ka aa ta ra 'bab pa //

T02TD2472E:148a-40: shes rab nang gi gsang ba'i dbang //
T02TD2472E:148a-41: slob ma rang gi lte ba can //
T02TD2472E:148a-43: rdul dang mun pa snying stobs te //
T02TD2472E:148a-45: spas pa'i gsang ba'i dbang du gsungs //
T02TD2472E:148a-46: gsang ba'i dbang la yang bzhi ste //
T02TD2472E:148a-47: rdo rje dang ni padma nas //

T02TD2472E:148a-49: yang na gong gi rim de nyid //

T02TD2472E:148a-51: bde chen lam sbyangs gsum pa'o //
T02TD2472E:148a-52: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa //
T02TD2472E:148b-0: ye @148b shes chen po bzhi pa'o //

T02TD2472E:148b-4: phyi yi padma ngag gi lam //

T02TD2472E:148b-6: sbas pa lte ba'i padma la'o //
T02TD2472E:148b-7: thabs ni gtso gzungs slob mar bcas //
T02TD2472E:148b-8: lus ngag sems la dri med cing //
T02TD2472E:148b-9: de ni mi phyed mthun pa yin //
T02TD2472E:148b-10: ngag gi sgrib pa des byang nas //
T02TD2472E:148b-11: ngag ni shin tu sbyangs pa ste //
T02TD2472E:148b-12: sangs rgyas sa ni dang po non //
T02TD2472E:148b-13: de yi man nang gsang ba'o //
T02TD2472E:148b-14: dgongs pa'i don dang nges don dang //

T02TD2472E:148b-19: thabs dang shes rab rtags su sbyar //
T02TD2472E:148b-20: nang gi sbas pa'i ngag brda dang //
T02TD2472E:148b-21: sbyor ba yi ni brdzi rnams dang //
T02TD2472E:148b-22: rim gyis mkha' 'gro'i brda skad bstan //
T02TD2472E:148b-23: sbom pos khro mo mnan pa ni //

T02TD2472E:148b-25: rdzas ni zla ba nyi ma dang //

T02TD2472E:148b-28: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kun //
T02TD2472E:148b-29: gtso gzungs zhal du thim pa las //
T02TD2472E:148b-30: sku yi dbus su thim pa dang //

T02TD2472E:148b-34: yab yum pa yi dang du gsal //
T02TD2472E:148b-35: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag ltar //
T02TD2472E:148b-36: thim pas sems gyur dgongs pa'i don //
T02TD2472E:148b-37: nus pa'i tshad kyang de bzhin du /
T02TD2472E:148b-38: ji snyed dag gi dri ma 'khru //
T02TD2472E:148b-39: buddha'i sar sgrib shin tu dag / shes rab thabs kyi nga rgyal byed //
T02TD2472E:148b-40: chos kun ro gcig shes par nus //
T02TD2472E:148b-41: sangs rgyas sa ni mngon du thob //
T02TD2472E:148b-42: thabs kyi phyag rgyas phung po 'joms //
T02TD2472E:148b-43: nyon mongs shes rab ma yin te //

T02TD2472E:148b-47: thabs ni skyes bu byed pa'i 'bras //

T02TD2472E:148b-49: rgyu mthun khu ba'i ngo bo yin //

T02TD2472E:148b-51: yab yum mnyes par mchod byas //
T02TD2472E:148b-52: dbang thob pa yi rgyu yin no //
T02TD2472E:148b-53: de nas gsum pa bshad pa bya ste //
T02TD2472E:149a-2: sngags kyi spyad pa spyod pa'i tshe //
T02TD2472E:149a-3: 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
T02TD2472E:149a-4: sngags dang dus sa dang rgyal ba las //
T02TD2472E:149a-5: bslang ste sbas pa'i don bstan pa //

T02TD2472E:149a-7: lus kyi ngo bo dgon pa la //
T02TD2472E:149a-8: byang chub sems kyi gnas bcas pa //
T02TD2472E:149a-9: bde ba'i stan yang gnas su bshad //
T02TD2472E:149a-10: dus ni dbang gnyis rdzogs pa dang //

T02TD2472E:149a-13: phyi yi bla ma'o nang rig ma //

T02TD2472E:149a-22: sbyangs dang sems bskyed byin rlabs dang //
T02TD2472E:149a-23: dbang bskur bla mas bya ba yin //

T02TD2472E:149a-27: sring mo grogs mo ma yin te //

T02TD2472E:149a-32: rnal 'byor ma ni so so med //

T02TD2472E:149a-35: rtsa yi 'dab ma gnas nas su //

T02TD2472E:149a-39: rtsa gsum mtshan nyid shes bya ste //

T02TD2472E:149a-43: chos gos rgyan chas ldan par bya //
T02TD2472E:149a-44: de la tshogs kyi ston mo dbul //
T02TD2472E:149a-45: chang yang drang ba byas nas ni //

T02TD2472E:149a-48: rdo rje padmo rnam gnyis kyang //

T02TD2472E:149a-51: 'jug pa'i tshul ni dben pa ru //

T02TD2472E:152b-27: 'bras bu'i nang na'ang bde mchog go //
T02TD2472E:152b-28: dbang gsum bye brag las grol phyir //
T02TD2472E:152b-29: bzhi pa'i dbang zhes grags ba ste //
T02TD2472E:152b-30: rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs kyi gsang //
T02TD2472E:152b-31: thams cad mkhyen par 'dir brjod do //
T02TD2472E:152b-32: 'on kyang kun mkhyen ma thob par //
T02TD2472E:152b-33: de nyid nye bar yang mi 'gyur //
T02TD2472E:152b-35: de nyid thob bya'i gnas su 'gyur //
T02TD2472E:152b-36: de las rim pa mchog yin pas //
T02TD2472E:152b-37: sgrub po rnams kyis nan tan bya'o //
T02TD2472E:152b-38: slob dpon rnams ni ma mnyes shing //
T02TD2472E:152b-39: dbang rnams rim gyis ma bgrod par //
T02TD2472E:152b-40: sngags spyod sgrub pa rtsom byed na //
T02TD2472E:152b-41: de 'bras med cing ngan song ltung //
T02TD2472E:152b-42: dbang rnams bgrod pa ma byas par //
T02TD2472E:152b-43: thugs thub ra chod sems kyis ni //
T02TD2472E:152b-44: gang dag man ngag rim bstan na //
T02TD2472E:152b-45: phung byed gnyis ka dmyal bar ltung //
T02TD2472E:152b-46: de ni sngags kyi dam tshig ces //
T02TD2472E:152b-47: smra byed lce la zhing rmo zhing //
T02TD2472E:152b-48: mnar med gnas su nye bar 'khor //
T02TD2472E:152b-49: dbang ma bgrod pa'i gang zag dag / gal te 'dri bas dge slong yang //
T02TD2472E:153a-0: @153a * // gtam gyi rigs tsam yang mi brjod //
T02TD2472E:153a-1: de brjod nyes pa'ang brjod mi lang //
T02TD2472E:153a-2: rim pa rdzogs shing snod can la //
T02TD2472E:153a-3: 'dri shing gleng slong byed pa na //
T02TD2472E:153a-4: de la de don ma bstan na //
T02TD2472E:153a-5: de yang nyes pa'i gnas su 'gyur //
T02TD2472E:153a-6: gang zhig dbang gi rim pa ni //
T02TD2472E:153a-7: bla ma gzhan las rdzogs blangs la //
T02TD2472E:153a-8: man ngag gi ni rim pa ni //
T02TD2472E:153a-9: bla ma gzhan las blang du rung //
T02TD2472E:153a-10: dbang dang man ngag ma bgrod par //
T02TD2472E:153a-11: glegs bam la brten shes rab kyis //
T02TD2472E:153a-12: gang zhig man ngag rim rnyed na //
T02TD2472E:153a-13: de ni sngon sbyangs 'phro can no //
T02TD2472E:153a-14: des kyang bla ma dag pa la //
T02TD2472E:153a-15: dbang gi rim pa bgrod par gces //
T02TD2472E:153a-16: rnam smin shes rab sbyangs pa'i mthus //
T02TD2472E:153a-17: lung ngag rtogs ba sbyangs pa dang //
T02TD2472E:153a-19: dbang ma bgrod la bstan gyur na //
T02TD2472E:153a-20: bdag kyang phung la gzhan yang brlag / de bas gzhan du bstan mi bya //
T02TD2472E:153a-21: bdag gis brtsams pa'i man ngag 'di //
T02TD2472E:153a-22: rim pa tshul bzhin bris pa yis //
T02TD2472E:153a-23: 'gro kun gsang sngags snod ldan te //
T02TD2472E:153a-24: tshe 'di nyid la byang chub shog //
T02TD2472E:153a-25: rin chen 'khor lo'i dbang gi man ngag gi rim pa slob dpon aaindra bh'u ti'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
